sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Controller as UserV1Controller
    participant Facade as UserFacade
    participant UserService
    participant DB

    %% 회원가입
    Note over User, DB: POST /api/v1/users (회원가입)

    User->>Controller: POST /api/v1/users (loginId, password, name, birthDate, email)
    Controller->>Facade: register(request)
    Facade->>UserService: register(loginId, password, name, birthDate, email)

    Note over UserService: UserModel 생성 시 도메인 규칙 검증
    alt 형식 검증 실패 (loginId·name·email·password·birthDate 규칙 위반)
        UserService-->>Facade: CoreException(BAD_REQUEST)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    end

    UserService->>DB: SELECT users WHERE user_id = loginId
    alt 중복 loginId
        UserService-->>Facade: CoreException(CONFLICT)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 409 Conflict
    end

    UserService->>UserService: BCrypt 암호화(password)
    UserService->>DB: INSERT users
    UserService-->>Facade: UserModel
    Facade-->>Controller: UserInfo
    Controller-->>User: 201 Created

    %% 내 정보 조회
    Note over User, DB: GET /api/v1/users/me (내 정보 조회)

    User->>Controller: GET /api/v1/users/me
    Note over Controller: Interceptor — loginId/loginPw 검증 후 UserModel 주입

    alt 유저 없음 또는 비밀번호 불일치
        Controller-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Controller->>Facade: getMe(userId)
    Facade->>UserService: getUser(userId)
    UserService->>DB: SELECT users WHERE id = userId
    UserService-->>Facade: UserModel
    Note over Facade: 이름 마지막 글자 * 마스킹
    Facade-->>Controller: UserInfo
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK ApiResponse(UserResponse)

    %% 비밀번호 변경
    Note over User, DB: PUT /api/v1/users/password (비밀번호 변경)

    User->>Controller: PUT /api/v1/users/password (currentPassword, newPassword)
    Note over Controller: Interceptor — loginId/loginPw 검증 후 UserModel 주입

    alt 유저 없음 또는 비밀번호 불일치
        Controller-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Controller->>Facade: changePassword(userId, currentPassword, newPassword)
    Facade->>UserService: changePassword(userId, currentPassword, newPassword)
    UserService->>DB: SELECT users WHERE id = userId

    alt 현재 비밀번호 불일치
        UserService-->>Facade: CoreException(BAD_REQUEST)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    else 새 비밀번호 = 현재 비밀번호
        UserService-->>Facade: CoreException(BAD_REQUEST)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    else 비밀번호 규칙 위반 (길이·생년월일 포함)
        UserService-->>Facade: CoreException(BAD_REQUEST)
        Facade-->>Controller: CoreException
        Controller-->>User: 400 Bad Request
    end

    UserService->>UserService: BCrypt 암호화(newPassword)
    UserService->>DB: UPDATE users SET password = ?
    UserService-->>Facade: UserModel
    Facade-->>Controller: UserInfo
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK
